www.veterinaryireland.ie &#xd;
Veterinary Ireland has six Interest Groups:&#xd;
&#xd;
Food Animal - Representing those Veterinary Practitioners providing veterinary services to the owners/ keepers of cattle (dairy and Beef), sheep, pigs, aquaculture, and poultry.&#xd;
&#xd;
Veterinary Ireland Companion Animal Society (VICAS)Representing those Veterinary Practitioners providing veterinary services to the owners/keepers of dogs, cats, and other companion animals.&#xd;
&#xd;
Equine&#xd;
Representing those Veterinary Practitioners providing veterinary services to the owners/keepers of equidae.&#xd;
&#xd;
Local Authority&#xd;
Representing those Veterinary Practitioners providing veterinary services on behalf of Irish Local Authorities.&#xd;
&#xd;
State Sector&#xd;
Representing those Veterinary Practitioners providing veterinary services on behalf of State Agencies.&#xd;
&#xd;
Education, Research &amp; Industry (ERI)&#xd;
Representing those Veterinary Practitioners providing veterinary services on behalf of Education, Research and Industry organisations.
